---
import Layout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Terms of Service',
  description: 'Terms of service for Dryspace Waterproofing',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="px-6 sm:px-6 py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-20 mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    <header>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-8 font-heading">
        Terms of Service
      </h1>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mb-8">Last updated: January 2025</p>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
      <p>By accessing our website and services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service and all applicable laws and regulations.</p>

      <h2>2. Services</h2>
      <p>Dryspace Waterproofing provides professional waterproofing, foundation repair, and related services in the Greater Toronto Area. All services are subject to availability and scheduling.</p>

      <h2>3. Warranty</h2>
      <p>We offer a 25-year transferable warranty on qualifying services. Specific warranty terms and conditions are provided separately with each service contract.</p>

      <h2>4. Payment Terms</h2>
      <p>Payment terms are specified in individual service agreements. We offer various financing options subject to credit approval.</p>

      <h2>5. Liability</h2>
      <p>Our liability is limited to the scope of work specified in the service agreement. We are fully licensed and insured for all services provided.</p>

      <h2>6. Emergency Services</h2>
      <p>24/7 emergency services are available. Emergency service rates may differ from standard rates.</p>

      <h2>7. Contact Information</h2>
      <p>For questions about these terms, please contact us at:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Phone: 437-545-0067</li>
        <li>Email: p.vysotckii@gmail.com</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>